    "client_msg_id": "6D7D7D52-E9F9-40E8-8108-A525482FA586",
    "text": "It's a \"lisp on the left\". I think it was _the_ tool I had in mind when I coined that term.\n\nSo I don't personally count it as visual programming. You aren't programming _through_ visuals, you're programming in text while looking at and lightly manipulating visual output.",
